snippet.title: Super Mario Gravity - Trailer
snippet.description:
Super Mario Gravity is a modification to Super Mario Galaxy 2, featuring brand new galaxies. This mod will feature over 30 galaxies and will be playable legally on any homebrew-enabled Wii or Wii U console.

Music by Trinkets' Toad Symphony. Check out his channel here!: https://youtube.com/channel/UCUIgfM8wyhIeELwUebteltw
And for the trailer's theme check here: https://youtu.be/pYgnAF8GB4U

Demo with 10 Stars: https://youtu.be/FG_uufkkAJo
*A new Demo is coming in May!*

Links:
Thread: https://gbatemp.net/threads/super-mario-gravity-smg2-mod.537951/
